sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Chat UI
  participant GW as Gateway
  participant US as user-service(chat routes)
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant RB as Redis cache/helpers
  participant BOT as chatbot-service
  participant AN as analytics-service

  UI->>GW: POST /api/user-chat/sessions/:id/messages
  GW->>US: forward request
  US->>US: validate owner(session.userId==token.userId)
  US->>DB: read session + append message metadata
  US->>BOT: generate response/recommendations
  BOT-->>US: AI reply
  US->>DB: update lastMessageAt/title heuristics
  US->>RB: cache/invalidate session list keys
  US->>AN: emit CHAT_MESSAGE_SENT + CHATBOT_QUERY
  US-->>UI: response payload with assistant message
